IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. SAMPLEVULN.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 API-KEY       PIC X(32) VALUE "sk_test_1234567890abcdef12345678".
01 DB-PASSWORD   PIC X(16) VALUE "SuperSecret123!".
01 WS-MESSAGE    PIC X(80).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    STRING
        "Connecting with API key: " DELIMITED BY SIZE
        API-KEY DELIMITED BY SIZE
        INTO WS-MESSAGE
    END-STRING

    DISPLAY WS-MESSAGE
    DISPLAY "DB password is configured."
    STOP RUN.
